title: George Formby - Turned Out Nice Again - 1941 [H666]
description:
George Pearson, who works for a underwear firm that is 20 years out of date, 
invests his own money in a new type of thread. The company are not interested 
in changes, and he is fired. Later the firm discover that the thread has 
revolutionized the garment industry, they move quickly, to hire him back, 
before the opposition hear the news, and make him a better offer.
